# TypeORM Integration This project is configured with **TypeORM** and **<%= database %>**. ##
Structure - `src/infrastructure/persistence/typeorm/entities/`: TypeORM specific `@Entity()`
definitions - `src/infrastructure/persistence/typeorm/repositories/`: Implements domain ports using
TypeORM's `Repository` - `src/infrastructure/persistence/typeorm/mappers/`: Transforms ORM entities
to/from Domain entities - `src/infrastructure/config/database.config.ts`: TypeORM data source
configuration for CLI migrations ## Commands Run migrations: \`\`\`bash npm run typeorm
migration:run -- -d src/infrastructure/config/database.config.ts \`\`\` Generate a new migration:
\`\`\`bash npm run typeorm migration:generate -- -d src/infrastructure/config/database.config.ts -n
migration_name \`\`\`
